Description: Property Index Number associated with exemption recipient
Date file was received by LexisNexis (sent by CCAO)
Original Record Type (A = ADD,C = Change, Blank)

Verified or Proof Code (V = Verified, P = Proof); this info is only provided on SSA records; Verified or V = Report verified with a family member or someone acting on behalf of a family member (i.e. Funeral home, etc.), Proof or P = Death Certificate Observed.
